      "versionNonce": 9849677,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772676956590,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5.1.1 Node Exporter\n\nThe Prometheus node exporter software is\ninstalled on all virtual machines which are\nmonitored for operating system metrics.\n\nIt exposesg metrics for Prometheus to pull on\nport 9100.\n\nThe node exporter is installed on all CBC nodes.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "JU_0xTWdtydhzCyZkeOn0",
      "originalText": "5.1.1 Node Exporter\n\nThe Prometheus node exporter software is installed on all virtual machines which are monitored for operating system metrics.\n\nIt exposesg metrics for Prometheus to pull on port 9100.\n\nThe node exporter is installed on all CBC nodes.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mVqScvcM3J1RkhzC1BEd5",
