      "updated": 1773124715972,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Site failover\n\nThese steps will take us from one site to the other for CBC \n\nSTANDBY CLUSTER: \n sudo su\n oramgr promote\n oramgr status\n\nACTIVE CLUSTER:\n make configure_geored_standby.yml \n\nverification:\n oramgr status\n pcs status\n\nRecovery:\n pcs resource refresh\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "yUmCpev4LKzQ0wdU2_Ho9",
      "originalText": "Site failover\n\nThese steps will take us from one site to the other for CBC \n\nSTANDBY CLUSTER: \n sudo su\n oramgr promote\n oramgr status\n\nACTIVE CLUSTER:\n make configure_geored_standby.yml \n\nverification:\n oramgr status\n pcs status\n\nRecovery:\n pcs resource refresh\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
