      "updated": 1773365160191,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cloud Execution Environment\n\nThe placeholder/dummy VMs were deployed directly\nonto Cloud Execution\nEnvironment rather than through Ericsson\nOrchestrator - Cloud Manager\n\nhttps://confluencecloud.tools.telstra.com/wiki/sp\naces/CCLBS/pages/687139\n562/Telco+Cloud+outage+scenarios\n\nfor example:\n\nhttps://cjy9-cee-nc-\n04.opnet.telstra.com.au/horizon/auth/login/",
